OL,3,CTerry Jones statue damaged by vandals
OL,4,Cless than a month after being unveiled
OL,6,FThe memorial statue of Monty Python
OL,7,Fstar, Terry Jones, has been vandalised
OL,8,Fless than a month since it was
OL,9,Funveiled.
OL,11,FThe bronze sculpture stands on Colwyn
OL,12,FBay's promenade and captures the late
OL,13,Factor's iconic moment as the show's
OL,14,Fnude organist.
OL,16,FWhile the statue avoided significant
OL,17,Fdamage, two door knockers were torn
OL,18,Foff.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
