OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1779379877
OL,3,CTerry Jones statue damaged by vandals
OL,4,Cless than a month after being unveiled
OL,6,FThese parts refer to animated
OL,7,Fcharacters from the 1986 fantasy film
OL,8,FLabyrinth, which Jones wrote.
OL,10,FThe statue's designer, Nick Elphick,
OL,11,Frevealed the damage.
OL,13,FIn a Facebook video, Elphick explained
OL,14,Fthe sculpture had suffered "slight
OL,15,Fvandalism", but bypassers had
OL,16,Fdiscovered the broken door knockers
OL,17,Fand safely returned them to him.
OL,19,FElphick also said he hopes to repair
OL,20,Fthe statue, but described the
OL,21,Fsituation as "very, very sad":
OL,26,@vD@\OUwD@JO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
