OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1779379877
OL,3,CTerry Jones statue damaged by vandals
OL,4,Cless than a month after being unveiled
OL,6,F"Can't believe it really, I'm actually
OL,7,Fgutted.J"But just to let everyone
OL,8,Fknow, there are CCTV cameras
OL,9,Fcompletely on it. So whoever's done
OL,10,Fit, will be seen."
OL,12,FThe iconic statue has attracted a
OL,13,Flarge number of tourists and seen
OL,14,Fvisits from celebrities including Sir
OL,15,FMichael Palin, Terry Gilliam, and Suzy
OL,16,FEddie Izzard.
OL,18,FMr Jones died in 2020 at the age of 77
OL,19,Ffollowing a rare form of dementia.
